Modifications in this fork Copyright (c) 2026 bybrave, licensed under the same
Apache License, Version 2.0. Changes from the original 0.12.0 release:
  - ANSI escape sequences rewritten from octal (\033) to hex (\x1b) so the
    source is valid in strict mode / ES modules (upstream issue #52); the
    rendered terminal output is byte-for-byte identical.
  - generate() now returns the rendered string in addition to invoking the
    callback / console.log (upstream issue #24).
  - Dual ESM + CommonJS packaging and bundled TypeScript type definitions
    (upstream issue #27).

